  "body": "We are using indices_for_slot across prysm, from proto definition to core logic. Let's do the following:\r\n\r\n- Inside crystallized field,  change `indices_for_slots` to `shard_and_committees`\r\n- Change `GetIndicesForSlot` to `GetShardAndCommitteesForSlot`\r\n\r\nIn the end, crystallized state contains an array of ShardAndCommittee struct. Within ShardAndCommittee struct, there's shard_id and committee combo that should be attesting at that slot. ",
